{"tid":870424,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解上證呢廿幾年來都無升過？","createTime":"2018-10-21T06:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T09:48:56.000Z","uid":9136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e26c2f164f46074424265d86dc346899bdbe5b","tid":870424,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T06:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/142349_2f7f08e1944b2fc883aaef382cf9f907.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F142349_2f7f08e1944b2fc883aaef382cf9f907.png&h=62b8b6eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/141053_da70fe64537313f2c73deca72b33298e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F141053_da70fe64537313f2c73deca72b33298e.png&h=5311d855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n08個頂（6124點）至今都未升返到 2017-2018大牛市又唔升 <br />\n依家上證竟然係2006年既水平<br />\n大陸既公司呢廿年唔會盈利既咩 照計個價值亦會因寬鬆政策而上升 <br />\n大陸樓呢廿年升左十倍 物價亦明顯升左 人工都係 但股市完全冇郁過咁濟<br />\n究竟係咩原因？<br />\n關唔關「中國股市85%係個人投資者，15%係機構」既事？<br />\n令到完全冇價值投資者，個個凈係炒股票，追漲殺跌？<br />\n諗下真係好誇張 股市係呢廿年竟然係原地踏步"},{"pid":"3a70b432ed5ea4907f8e79f0bb897218d9346a8f","tid":870424,"uid":28163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"大陸人淨係識炒樓<br />\n股市 邊個識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b41cf92eb5951bfa92dfa0e998937d774a0572","tid":870424,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/143323_95ff571cd64dcf4f387b3cb826004466.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F143323_95ff571cd64dcf4f387b3cb826004466.png&h=bf22c81c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全唔知點理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\